OL,6,FA drink-driver who lost control of her
OL,7,Fvehicle and struck a university
OL,8,Fstudent waiting at a bus shelter, has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FEmma Roberts crashed a black Jaguar
OL,12,Fthrough a bus shelter on the A270
OL,13,FLewes Road in Brighton, leaving a man
OL,14,Fin his 20s with life-threatening
OL,15,Finjuries.
OL,17,FThe incident took place at 11.55pm on
OL,18,F6 September 2023 - Roberts had reached
OL,19,F74mph in a 30mph zone before the
OL,20,Fimpact.
