OL,6,FRoberts was arrested at the scene,
OL,7,Fwhere an evidential breath test found
OL,8,Fshe was more than three times the
OL,9,Falcohol limit while driving.
OL,11,FRoberts, 43, of Church Street,
OL,12,FReigate, earlier pleaded guilty to the
OL,13,Fcharge in September 2023.
OL,15,FAt Lewes Crown Court on Thursday, 10
OL,16,FOctober, Roberts was sentenced for
OL,17,Fcausing serious injuries by dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving.
