OL,6,FShe was sentenced to two years and
OL,7,Ffour months in prison and was
OL,8,Fdisqualified for three years and two
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FPolice say drink-driving and speeding
OL,12,Fare some of the main factors in why
OL,13,Fpeople are killed or seriously injured
OL,14,Fon roads.
OL,16,FSpeaking after the case, investigating
OL,17,Fofficer Jade Smith from the Serious
OL,18,FCollision Investigation Unit said:
OL,19,F"This again demonstrates the dangers
OL,20,Fof drink-driving.
