OL,6,F"Roberts was incredibly fortunate that
OL,7,Fher reckless behaviour did not cause a
OL,8,Ffatality that night.
OL,10,F"She risked her own safety as well as
OL,11,Fthe safety of the public.
OL,13,F"So we are pleased that a dangerous
OL,14,Fdriver has been taken off our roads.
OL,15,FWe are determined to catch dangerous
OL,16,Fdrivers, and this case should act as a
OL,17,Fwarning to others about the dangers of
OL,18,Fdrink driving and driving at excessive
OL,19,Fspeed."
