OL,6,FThe court heard from the victim, who
OL,7,Fsaid the vehicle had swerved towards
OL,8,Fhim, leaving him no time to react.
OL,10,FHe described seeing Roberts' black
OL,11,FJaguar out of control on the A270,
OL,12,Fnear the junction with Barcombe Road.
OL,13,FShe was seen swerving in the
OL,14,Fcarriageway.
OL,16,FHe described waking in hospital in
OL,17,F"constant agony" after being in a coma
OL,18,Fand having to undergo multiple
OL,19,Fsurgeries.
